{"tid":657850,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[Ben家有女初長成]囡囡已經21歲 許紹雄：佢夠運似阿媽","createTime":"2018-05-08T12:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T01:32:24.000Z","uid":157545,"like":64,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"302184848abeb25a5e65960868fdce94c101034c","tid":657850,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180508/large/1525753599_5e06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180508%2Flarge%2F1525753599_5e06.jpg&h=e659cee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又一個靚靚星二代登場！<br />\n人稱Benz雄嘅許紹雄，喺92年同新加坡籍嘅太太結婚後，生咗一個囡囡Charmaine，唔經唔覺，囡囡今年已經21歲，向來都低調家事嘅Benz雄，噚日喺網上貼咗啲幾張家庭相，原來佢為囡囡搞咗個生日party，請咗韓馬利、羅樂林、陳志健同埋老婆等等，Benz仲留言話：「我女兒Charmaine，祝你生日快樂、身體健康！」<br />\n<br />\nCharmaine亦有喺網上轉發相片，佢仲留言話：「好多謝大家出席我嘅生日party，我知道大家都好期待party啲相，不過要俾小小時間去整，我愛你哋，我21歲喇！」睇見佢哋一家三口嘅合照，又真係好溫馨，佘詩曼亦都有留言祝佢生日快樂。<br />\n<br />\n之前Benz雄曾經喺訪問講過，囡囡Charmaine喺浸會大學讀傳理系三年級，平時係太太管教，佢就負責陪玩，佢又話囡囡本身對娛樂圈嘅工作冇興趣，所以冇諗過入行！<br />\n<br />\n原來Benz雄囡囡係前日正日21歲生日，一家人就喺上星期六同佢搞party慶祝。《蘋果》今日打俾Benz雄，佢話已經飛咗去北京做嘢喇！當記者大讚佢個女越大越靚，Benz雄即刻好開心笑住話:「多謝多謝，佢夠運，唔似我，似媽咪。」Benz雄話囡囡讀埋今年就大學畢業，問個女有冇拍拖，佢話:「後生女拍拖呢啲梗有㗎啦，咁大個女，佢鍾意點就點，我唔會管佢嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180508/large/1525753602_2146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180508%2Flarge%2F1525753602_2146.jpg&h=7a9386c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180508/large/1525753604_c948.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180508%2Flarge%2F1525753604_c948.jpg&h=651b093a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180508/large/1525753605_26a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180508%2Flarge%2F1525753605_26a9.jpg&h=04d98d71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"296be7889c54159876f55623b466ff3d2c0ac149","tid":657850,"uid":35930,"like":50,"dislike":8,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"八字波"},{"pid":"bdc35cbfa919b2c2ddc31a31b3d741bcc4e506d6","tid":657850,"uid":51387,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"靚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f99f6c3a512902d6730ffdb140f9b9265f0492e","tid":657850,"uid":153400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T12:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c7f773510cb6165d325fb8954403e31149e850","tid":657850,"uid":181819,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"Tesla雄"},{"pid":"a5ec27117d20d3b88a18a7855283419c9a843ab3","tid":657850,"uid":39710,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"容海恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf3e603a0aaa78e6c803be3ad8f05c6a010bb5f","tid":657850,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"係bu好似見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a89ee44771651ed6f3fa9f23628ad2c48f686a","tid":657850,"uid":55511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得似一個人又講唔出似邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41fdd273ed02a9ff10608ffba5145f301769cc6","tid":657850,"uid":157545,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"16a89ee44771651ed6f3fa9f23628ad2c48f686a","tid":657850,"uid":55511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得似一個人又講唔出似邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces